      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "你有没有想过，人口是如何增长的？放射性物质是如何衰变的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.5,
      "size": 40032,
      "text": "这些问题都涉及到变化率，而微分方程正是描述变化率的数学语言。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.39,
      "size": 22176,
      "text": "今天我们将探索这个强大的数学工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "微分方程是包含未知函数及其导数的方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "常微分方程只涉及一个自变量，通常是时间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "解微分方程就是找到满足方程的函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "初始条件决定了众多解中的特定一个。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-1",
      "filename": "exponential-exp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/exponential-exp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "最简单的微分方程是：变化率与当前值成正比。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-2",
      "filename": "exponential-exp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/exponential-exp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "如果比例常数为正，得到指数增长，如细菌繁殖。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-3",
