      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/exponential-exp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "如果比例常数为负，得到指数衰减，如放射性衰变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "exponential",
      "line_id": "exp-4",
      "filename": "exponential-exp-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ode/exponential-exp-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "这个方程的解是指数函数，是自然界中最常见的模式之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ode",
      "section_id": "oscillation",
      "line_id": "osc-1",
